{
  "page": "Alys Turnberry",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Turnberry\" title=\"House Turnberry\"><img alt=\"House Turnberry.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/04/House_Turnberry.svg/50px-House_Turnberry.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/04/House_Turnberry.svg/75px-House_Turnberry.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/04/House_Turnberry.svg/100px-House_Turnberry.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Alys Turnberry</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Pryor\" title=\"House Pryor\"><img alt=\"House Pryor.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2f/House_Pryor.svg/50px-House_Pryor.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2f/House_Pryor.svg/75px-House_Pryor.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2f/House_Pryor.svg/100px-House_Pryor.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Saera_targaryen%27s_sweet_little_fool_by_viscardiac.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Saera targaryen&#39;s sweet little fool by viscardiac.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/38/Saera_targaryen%27s_sweet_little_fool_by_viscardiac.png/350px-Saera_targaryen%27s_sweet_little_fool_by_viscardiac.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/38/Saera_targaryen%27s_sweet_little_fool_by_viscardiac.png/525px-Saera_targaryen%27s_sweet_little_fool_by_viscardiac.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/38/Saera_targaryen%27s_sweet_little_fool_by_viscardiac.png/700px-Saera_targaryen%27s_sweet_little_fool_by_viscardiac.png 2x\" /></a><div>Alys Turnberry, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://viscardiac.tumblr.com/\">viscardiac</a></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nSweetberry<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady of <a href=\"/index.php/Pebble\" title=\"Pebble\">Pebble</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Turnberry\" title=\"House Turnberry\">House Turnberry</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Pryor\" title=\"House Pryor\">House Pryor</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_67_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">67&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Dunstan_Pryor\" title=\"Dunstan Pryor\">Dunstan Pryor</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">Bastard</a> daughter<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Alys Turnberry</b>, called <b>Sweetberry</b>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_companion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady companion\">lady companion</a> to Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Saera_Targaryen\" title=\"Saera Targaryen\">Saera Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alys_Turnberry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> considered Alys to be a pretty, vapid, empty-headed little fool, from what she had seen of her. Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Elysar\" title=\"Elysar\">Elysar</a> called her a <a href=\"http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/trull\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikt:trull\">trull</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alys_Turnberry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Alys was a <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maiden</a> of an age with Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Saera_Targaryen\" title=\"Saera Targaryen\">Saera Targaryen</a>, attending the royal court at the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. In <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_82_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">82&#160;AC</a>, Alys became a favorite and dearest friend of the princess, along with <a href=\"/index.php/Perianne_Moore\" title=\"Perianne Moore\">Perianne Moore</a>. Saera nicknamed Alys <i>\"Sweetberry\"</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Saera and her five favorites — Alys, Perianne, <a href=\"/index.php/Jonah_Mooton\" title=\"Jonah Mooton\">Jonah Mooton</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roy_Connington\" title=\"Roy Connington\">Roy Connington</a>, and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Braxton_Beesbury\" title=\"Braxton Beesbury\">Braxton Beesbury</a>, called Stinger — became inseparable at every feast and ball. They hunted and <a href=\"/index.php/Hawk\" title=\"Hawk\">hawked</a> together, and once sailed across <a href=\"/index.php/Blackwater_Bay\" title=\"Blackwater Bay\">Blackwater Bay</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> together. When the young lords <a href=\"/index.php/Ride_at_rings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ride at rings\">rode at rings</a> or crossed swords in the yards, the three girls cheered them on. King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> was pleased at his daughter's popularity and friendship, but Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> was concerned about the character of Alys, Perianne, and the three boys. Nevertheless, King Jaehaerys felt they could not get up to trouble, with all the servants attending them watching.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_84_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">84&#160;AC</a>, an incident occurred between Saera's male favorites and <a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Turnip\" title=\"Tom Turnip\">Tom Turnip</a>, King Jaehaerys's <a href=\"/index.php/Fool\" title=\"Fool\">fool</a>, at the <a href=\"/index.php/Blue_Pearl\" title=\"Blue Pearl\">Blue Pearl</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Brothel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brothel\">brothel</a> in King's Landing, something Jonah claimed had been the princess's idea. Alys and Perianne were woken in the middle of the night and questioned by Queen Alysanne, telling them to tell the truth or they would join their male friends in the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep#Dungeon\" title=\"Red Keep\">dungeons</a>. Before long, the girls were weeping and pleading for forgiveness, although their confessions said almost nothing about the incident they were being questioned about. Perianne explained that Saera had been teaching Alys how to kiss, and she asked to be taught to kiss too, to train for their future marriages. Alys revealed that one night the girls had started kissing each other with their clothes off, taking turns pretending they were boys. Then, Saera dared Alys to kiss a real boy, and she dared Perianne, and both dared Saera, who said she would kiss a man grown, a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>. This began the ladies' affairs with Red Roy, Jonah, and Stinger. Perianne explained that Stinger did the \"training\" for all of them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Queen Alysanne then demanded to know where their <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septas</a> and servants had been during all of this. Perianne, confused, explained that servants do what you tell them, and they had sent them out of the room. As for the ones who knew, Stinger had threatened to <a href=\"/index.php/Tongue_mutilation\" title=\"Tongue mutilation\">have their tongues out</a> if they talked. This caused Alys to break down, sobbing and tearing at her dressing gown. She apologized to the queen, and claimed that Saera and Stinger had pressured her into sexual behavior. She revealed she was with child, and that she did not know who the father was. Alysanne sent both girls to bed, and told them that the next morning they would make a confession to a septa and be forgiven by <a href=\"/index.php/Mother_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Mother (the Seven)\">the Mother</a>. Alys knew that her own mother would not forgive her, however.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Hasty <a href=\"/index.php/Marriage\" title=\"Marriage\">marriages</a> were arranged for the two girls. However, Roy Connington refused to marry Alys, declaring that she was pregnant with Stinger's child, whom he would not make heir to <a href=\"/index.php/Griffin%27s_Roost\" title=\"Griffin&#39;s Roost\">Griffin's Roost</a> and raise as his own. Alys was sent to the <a href=\"/index.php/Motherhouse_of_Maris\" title=\"Motherhouse of Maris\">Motherhouse of Maris</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a>, where she gave birth to a girl with bright red hair like Roy's. Afterwards, she was wed to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Dunstan_Pryor\" title=\"Dunstan Pryor\">Dunstan Pryor</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Pebble\" title=\"Pebble\">Pebble</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alys_Turnberry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>We never meant to be wicked, we were only playing.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Alys, to Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Alysanne:</b> All you can do tonight is go to bed. On the morrow we shall send a <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septa</a> to you, and you can make confession of your sins. <a href=\"/index.php/Mother_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Mother (the Seven)\">The Mother</a> will forgive you.<br />\n<b>Alys:</b> <i>My</i> mother won't.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> and Alys</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Alysanne:</b> I have been speaking with your... <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_companion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady companion\">ladies</a>. Are you aware that Alys Turnberry is with child?<br />\n<b>Saera:</b> My Sweetberry? Truly? She... oh, what has she done? Oh, my sweet little fool.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Saera_Targaryen\" title=\"Saera Targaryen\">Saera Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alys_Turnberry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.07</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\">1.08</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\">1.09</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\">1.10</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\">1.11</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\">1.12</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-13\">1.13</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne: Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Alys_Turnberry\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Alys Turnberry</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403165120\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.148 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.428 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1588/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11155/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 15752/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2288/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4275/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.270/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.56 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  399.440      1 -total\n 91.70%  366.306      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 91.39%  365.065      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.63%   50.436     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  7.74%   30.909     14 Template:Ref\n  6.13%   24.493      6 Template:Infobox_label\n  4.58%   18.275     14 Template:Ref/core\n  3.16%   12.634      3 Template:Date\n  2.11%    8.425      3 Template:Quote\n  1.14%    4.566      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:25218-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403165120 and revision id 320949\n -->\n",
